# Backend Project

A YouTube-like backend

## Live API

Base URL: https://backend-project-0o08.onrender.com

Health endpoint:

- GET `/api/v1/`

## What's this?

Basically a video platform backend with:

- User signup/login (JWT auth with access & refresh tokens)
- Video uploads via Cloudinary
- Subscriptions (like YouTube's subscribe feature)
- MongoDB for storing everything

## Tech Stack

- Node.js + Express
- MongoDB + Mongoose
- Cloudinary (for video/image uploads)
- JWT for auth
- bcrypt for password hashing
- multer for file handling

## Setup

1. Clone it
2. `cd Backend && npm install`
3. Copy `.env.sample` to `.env` and fill in your stuff:
   - MongoDB connection string
   - Cloudinary credentials
   - JWT secrets (just make up some random strings)
4. `npm start`

## API Routes

### Health

| Method | Route      | Auth | What it does                              |
| ------ | ---------- | ---- | ----------------------------------------- |
| GET    | `/api/v1/` | No   | Health check. Returns API running status. |

### Users

Base: `/api/v1/users`

| Method | Route              | Auth | What it does                                                     |
| ------ | ------------------ | ---- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| POST   | `/register`        | No   | Register a new user with avatar and optional cover image upload. |
| POST   | `/login`           | No   | Login user and issue tokens.                                     |
| POST   | `/logout`          | Yes  | Logout current user.                                             |
| POST   | `/refresh-token`   | No   | Refresh access token using refresh token.                        |
| POST   | `/change-password` | Yes  | Change password for logged-in user.                              |
| GET    | `/current-user`    | Yes  | Get current user profile.                                        |
| PATCH  | `/update-account`  | Yes  | Update account fields.                                           |
| PATCH  | `/avatar`          | Yes  | Update avatar image.                                             |
| PATCH  | `/cover-image`     | Yes  | Update cover image.                                              |
| GET    | `/c/:username`     | Yes  | Get channel profile by username.                                 |
| GET    | `/history`         | Yes  | Get watch history for current user.                              |

### Tweets

Base: `/api/v1/tweet`

| Method | Route       | Auth | What it does                   |
| ------ | ----------- | ---- | ------------------------------ |
| POST   | `/`         | Yes  | Create tweet.                  |
| GET    | `/`         | Yes  | Get tweets for logged-in user. |
| PATCH  | `/:tweetId` | Yes  | Update tweet.                  |
| DELETE | `/:tweetId` | Yes  | Delete tweet.                  |

### Comments

Base: `/api/v1/comment`

| Method | Route                  | Auth | What it does              |
| ------ | ---------------------- | ---- | ------------------------- |
| GET    | `/:videoId`            | No   | Get comments for a video. |
| POST   | `/:videoId`            | Yes  | Add a comment to a video. |
| PATCH  | `/:videoId/:commentId` | Yes  | Update a comment.         |
| DELETE | `/:videoId/:commentId` | Yes  | Delete a comment.         |

### Likes

Base: `/api/v1/like`

| Method | Route                  | Auth | What it does               |
| ------ | ---------------------- | ---- | -------------------------- |
| POST   | `/toggle/v/:videoId`   | No   | Toggle like for a video.   |
| POST   | `/toggle/c/:commentId` | No   | Toggle like for a comment. |
| POST   | `/toggle/t/:tweetId`   | No   | Toggle like for a tweet.   |
| GET    | `/videos`              | No   | Get liked videos list.     |

### Subscriptions

Base: `/api/v1/subscriptions`

| Method | Route                 | Auth | What it does                                      |
| ------ | --------------------- | ---- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| POST   | `/toggle/:channelId`  | Yes  | Subscribe/unsubscribe current user for a channel. |
| GET    | `/channel/:channelId` | No   | Get subscriber list for a channel.                |
| GET    | `/user/:subscriberId` | No   | Get channels subscribed by a user.                |

### Playlists

Base: `/api/v1/playlist`

| Method | Route                          | Auth | What it does                |
| ------ | ------------------------------ | ---- | --------------------------- |
| POST   | `/`                            | Yes  | Create playlist.            |
| GET    | `/user/:userId`                | Yes  | Get playlists by user.      |
| GET    | `/:playlistId`                 | Yes  | Get playlist by id.         |
| PATCH  | `/:playlistId`                 | Yes  | Update playlist.            |
| DELETE | `/:playlistId`                 | Yes  | Delete playlist.            |
| PATCH  | `/add/:playlistId/:videoId`    | Yes  | Add video to playlist.      |
| PATCH  | `/remove/:playlistId/:videoId` | Yes  | Remove video from playlist. |

### Videos

Base: `/api/v1/video`

| Method | Route                      | Auth | What it does                                                  |
| ------ | -------------------------- | ---- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| GET    | `/`                        | Yes  | Get all videos (query/filter/pagination logic in controller). |
| POST   | `/`                        | Yes  | Publish a new video with thumbnail upload.                    |
| GET    | `/v/:videoId`              | Yes  | Get video by id.                                              |
| DELETE | `/v/:videoId`              | Yes  | Delete video by id.                                           |
| PATCH  | `/v/:videoId`              | Yes  | Update video and thumbnail.                                   |
| PATCH  | `/toggle/publish/:videoId` | Yes  | Toggle video publish status.                                  |

### Dashboard

Base: `/api/v1/dashboard`

| Method | Route             | Auth | What it does               |
| ------ | ----------------- | ---- | -------------------------- |
| GET    | `/stats/:userId`  | Yes  | Get channel stats summary. |
| GET    | `/videos/:userId` | Yes  | Get channel videos list.   |

## Notes

- Auth means JWT-protected route (`verifyJWT`).
- File uploads use multipart form-data on relevant routes.
- Route behavior is documented from current route/controller wiring in the codebase.

